    "This tier is likely to be useful for instructing students on AI literacy and AI usage, and more generally demonstrating the dangers of stochastic models.",
    "This tier has limited value to scholarly, peer-reviewed publications, as the principle of authorship and the requisite of originality (at least as currently conceived) would likely be violated by, for example, a systematic review conducted solely by an AI agent.",
